{"word":"κατάγω","slug":"κατάγω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ϰατάγω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:κατά\">κατά</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἄγω\">ἄγω</a></el>] <b>bring down<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp> <a href='B:510 9:30'>Ac 9:30</a>; <a href='B:510 22:30'>22:30</a>; <a href='B:510 23:15'>23:15</a>, <a href='B:510 23:20'>20</a>, <a href='B:510 23:28'>28</a>; <a href='B:520 10:6'>Ro 10:6</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> as nautical term, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> the idea of descent from the ‘high seas’, a boat <b><a href='B:490 5:11'>Lk 5:11</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pass.\">pass.</a> in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ act.\">act.</a> sense <b>put in, land <a href='B:510 21:3'>Ac 21:3</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>; <a href='B:510 27:3'>27:3</a>; <a href='B:510 28:12'>28:12</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:καταγράφω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:καταγωνίζομαι\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}